From: Alban Guillemot <alban@fullsteamconsulting.com.au <mailto:alban@fullsteamconsulting.com.au>>
Date: Monday, 1 March 2021 at 8:00 am
To: Madeleine Ryan <madeleine@advantagestyling.com.au <mailto:madeleine@advantagestyling.com.au>>
Subject: Re: Renta Centre New Website Testing

Hi Madeleine,

Thanks for sharing. The new site looks great.

We have done a SEO audit and noticed a few things to fix, especially on the homepage.

1) Homepage: The code used would need to be tweaked, especially heading tags, so we can achieve the best results SEO-wise. I have marked the recommendations in the PDF attached. Could you please share with the developer to fix?
2) Category pages (i.e. https://rentacentre2020.wpperk.cloud/rent/electronics/ <https://aus01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Frentacentre2020.wpperk.cloud%2Frent%2Felectronics%2F&data=04%7C01%7Cmadeleine%40advantagestyling.com.au%7C63afe8877d224a837b4708d8dc2bd6de%7C990eae31a9404d14b2ac18d698fa2459%7C1%7C0%7C637501428455612019%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C1000&sdata=Q%2BSBEcmlg6TfUd4HG2aW883%2B9o2%2Fj6wzG6tDgpe6mYk%3D&reserved=0>): Code is great, however all these pages dont have optimise meta data (i.e. page titles and meta description). Could you please ask the developer to copy and paste the metadata from the current site for each appropriate page?
3) Products pages: Overall they are great, however we noticed the code does not use product schema. Schema is really important, especially for products, so I would strongly advise to use. Could you please ask the developer to add product markup on all product pages. All the requirements are outlined here: https://developers.google.com/search/docs/data-types/product <https://aus01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.google.com%2Fsearch%2Fdocs%2Fdata-types%2Fproduct&data=04%7C01%7Cmadeleine%40advantagestyling.com.au%7C63afe8877d224a837b4708d8dc2bd6de%7C990eae31a9404d14b2ac18d698fa2459%7C1%7C0%7C637501428455612019%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C1000&sdata=pFaEp%2FCLFQpd1D83262yNzXbqpH9Cp9w2PPRWVNk%2FH0%3D&reserved=0>
4) Blog page: The page would need a few tweaks in terms of code (see PDF attached)
5) URL redirects: It appears that URLs have not changed across the board, which is great. We have however noticed several pages with different URLs. Before going live, it would be great to set 301 permanent redirects for these pages.
